data.description: Great location, Beautiful well maintained 3 BR / 2.5 BA home. Recently updated freshly painted interior and exterior. Main level has a 2-story entrance Foyer, Arched doorways in the Living Room and into the kitchen. It has a large living room with a very nice stone fireplace. It's an Open Kitchen floor plan with stained cabinets, granite counter tops, tile backsplash, kitchen overlooks the Living Room. The stairs lead up to loft that could be used as an office, TV room or a second family room. Master Bedroom includes a trey ceiling, Sitting Area, private bath with separate shower and garden tub, two sinks, and walk-in closet. Relax or entertain on the patio in your private fenced backyard. NEW HVAC System Great Location near, GA Gwinnett College, shopping, downtown, entertainment, and parks. Low HOA and no rental restrictions.
